<p>Welcome to the revamped version of Azure Storage web explorer</p>
@if (Utils.Util.Provider != "Azure")
{
	<p><b>Congratulations! ðŸ¥³ you just found a new hidden feature that allows you to manage your @Utils.Util.Provider objects</b></p>
